name: Discover first dataset
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nrouyer/assemblylineplanning/refs/heads/main/dataset/rotorcraft_assemblyline_20tasks.csv" AS row
RETURN row LIMIT 5

name: GDS DAG algorithms
query:
CALL gds.list() 
YIELD name, description, signature
WHERE toLower(name) CONTAINS "gds.dag"
RETURN name, description, signature
